4Geeks Academy offers a comprehensive Data Science & Machine Learning bootcamp designed for individuals with no prior experience. Over 16 weeks, students attend three classes weekly, with a maximum of 12 participants per class. The curriculum covers Python, SQL, statistics, and popular libraries such as Pandas and Numpy, focusing on creating predictive models and understanding machine learning algorithms. Students will engage in real-life projects and learn to manage AI project lifecycles. Certificates from the program are recognized by multiple organizations. Classes are available in English and Spanish. 

